## üó∫Ô∏è Roadmap

Phaeton is currently in **Beta (v0.2.0)**. Here is the status of our development pipeline:

| Feature | Status | Notes |
| :--- | :---: | :--- |
| **Parallel Streaming Engine** | ‚úÖ Ready | Powered by Rayon |
| **Smart Type Casting** | ‚úÖ Ready | Auto-clean numeric strings |
| **Quarantine Logic** | ‚úÖ Ready | Audit logs for bad data |
| **Fuzzy Alignment** | ‚úÖ Ready | Jaro-Winkler / Levenshtein |
| **SHA-256 Hashing** | üìù Planned | Security for PII data |
| **Column Splitting & Combining** | üìù Planned | - |
| **Imputation (`.fill()`)** | üìù Planned | Mean/Median/Mode fill |
| **Parquet/Arrow Integration** | üìù Planned | Native output support |

